sec.p:
To quantify the PAEE and effect of Tb on TEE, these data were analyzed with a physiological model33. Ta > 33 °C data were used to eliminate the contribution of cold-induced thermogenesis. The original model was slightly modified by combining the thermic effect of food and basal metabolic rate (BMR) into a resting metabolic rate (RMR) term, yielding Eq. 1:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
